com.Spal.C7_Question7helper

Class Billing

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.Spal.C7_Question7helper.Billing

  • public class Billing
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the class billing which will assign a value to bill the patient with for each doctor's visit. Now this class contains an object of the patient class and an object of the doctors class in which the program will associate a patient with the doctor object.
